Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\bord0\fad(1500,500)\pos(190,175)}彻夜难眠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\bord0\fad(1500,500)}编剧：史蒂文·莫法特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,还是不敢相信 我竟然有权利养他\N{\fs14}I still can't believe I'm allowed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他是你儿子啊\N{\fs14}He's your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是想说这个\N{\fs14}That's what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 谁批准这事的\N{\fs14}I mean, who authorized this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我遇到的最可怕的事情了\N{\fs14}It's the single most terrifying thing that's ever happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 我把他碰坏了怎么办\N{\fs14}I mean, what if I break him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,最好尽力别让它发生\N{\fs14}Yeah, you best try not to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你好吗 小家伙\N{\fs14}You all right, mate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.28,0:00:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧 没反应\N{\fs14}See? Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他没事的 他很爱你的\N{\fs14}He's fine. He loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吗\N{\fs14}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs14}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,只是每次我看着他的眼睛\N{\fs14}It's just when I look into his eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我接下来的六十年可能做错的事\N{\fs14}I see everything I'm going to do wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.12,0:00:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就全都浮现到我的眼前\N{\fs14}for the next 60 years reflected back at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你会是一个好爸爸的\N{\fs14}You're going to be an amazing dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你是一个很棒的人\N{\fs14}'cause you're an amazing man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 挺好的\N{\fs14}Huh? That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.39,0:01:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还没坏\N{\fs14}Still not broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,又一个 你听说这些消失的人了吗\N{\fs14}Another one. Have you seen all these people disappearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.68,0:01:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你能完全确定吗\N{\fs14}And you're absolutely sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他单独放在一起\N{\fs14}Me and him on our own
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.65,0:01:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,整整一周\N{\fs14}for a whole weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了 最坏能坏到哪儿去呢\N{\fs14}Of course, what is the worst that could happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.34,0:01:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,别说这句话\N{\fs14}Don't ever say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,说了这句话就一定会发生坏事\N{\fs14}If you say that, terrible things will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你没看见电影里都这样吗\N{\fs14}Have you never seen a film?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.28,0:01:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 该洗澡了\N{\fs14}Come on, it's his bath time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 我们昨天才给他洗过\N{\fs14}What? We literally just did that yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 拜托 别再大惊小怪了\N{\fs14}Oh, for God's sake, stop your fussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会没事的\N{\fs14}Everything is going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只是湿个手肘而已 又不是世界末日\N{\fs14}It's wet elbows, not the end of the world. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们带你去洗澡了\N{\fs14}Fine. Let's get you in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你不在的时候我也得给他洗澡吗\N{\fs14}Do I have to bath him while you're gone?
